      <title>Patron 为陷入困境的欧洲房地产投资筹集了 8.6 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/patron-raises-860-million-for-distressed-european-property-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Patron Capital 为其第七支欧洲房地产基金筹集了 8.6 亿欧元（9.27 亿美元），该公司寻求利用欧洲大陆房地产危机中出现的越来越多的不良资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/patron-raises-860-million-for-distressed-european-property-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
